                     <interp inst="t17850914-86-off428" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17850914-86-cd429" type="crimeDate">9th day of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850914-86-off428 t17850914-86-cd429"></join>, one woman's cloth cloak, value 5 s. and one tea spoon, value 12 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17850914-86-victim945" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Clifton
                  <interp inst="t17850914-86-victim945" type="surname" value="Clifton"></interp>
